{"tid":2500598,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【開創先河】西營盤日式居酒屋Okra 成為全港首間接受加密貨幣餐廳","createTime":"2021-04-22T18:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T19:20:01.000Z","uid":212249,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a422eb76e2e75b93eb789a09f3004368ac1beaa0","tid":2500598,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T18:56:52.000Z","msg":"隨住全球最大加密貨幣平台Coinbase Commerce於美國納斯達克市場上市，日式居酒屋Okra主廚Max Levy對加密貨幣前景充滿信心，為客人提供加密貨幣電子支付方式，成為全港首間亦係暫時唯一一間能夠用加密貨幣畀錢嘅餐廳。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/data/attachment/object_pic/2021/4/21/66586573cbd745416572ed70017d99b5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fobject_pic%2F2021%2F4%2F21%2F66586573cbd745416572ed70017d99b5.JPG&h=830468ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n餐廳老闆兼主廚Max Levy表示，「我哋一直致力利用社交媒體以外嶄新科技，為客人塑造更稱心滿意嘅體驗。隨住電子貨幣及區塊鏈科技不斷發展，有助業界節省銀行同信用卡公司所收取嘅高昂交易費用，同時亦能夠令客人有更好嘅支付模式。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/data/attachment/object_pic/2021/4/21/5ddfc5bb53662e3e73cc982090fe09f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fobject_pic%2F2021%2F4%2F21%2F5ddfc5bb53662e3e73cc982090fe09f7.jpg&h=cc68be98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nOkra現正接受客人以比特幣、比特幣（BTC）、以太幣（ETH）、幣安幣（BNB）、幣安幣美元（BUSD）和瑞波幣（XRP）支付等值港元款項，不過就無得用Elon Musk最鍾意嘅無狗狗幣（DOGE）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/data/attachment/object_pic/2021/4/21/1633d3bc223345006c3e06e4706981de.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fobject_pic%2F2021%2F4%2F21%2F1633d3bc223345006c3e06e4706981de.JPG&h=50555b22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nOkra表示為咗推出香港科技轉型，現時顧客只要用加密貨幣結帳，就可享有全單95折優惠，所慳返嘅5%正正就係客人用信用畀錢時商戶所支付嘅手續費。餐牌上所有價錢會以港元列示，客人畀錢嗰陣餐廳將會提供匯率資料。"},{"pid":"3fb2bfa37dd5c65abd21875363387f7e04e633bf","tid":2500598,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T18:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass